## 1. Tech Stack (What You Built It With)

| Layer | Technology | Version |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| **Backend Framework** | Laravel | 12 |
| **Frontend Framework** | Vue.js (SPA feel) | 3.4 |
| **Backend ‚Üî Frontend Bridge** | Inertia.js | 2.0 |
| **CSS Framework** | Tailwind CSS | 3.4 |
| **Database** | MySQL | - |
| **Build Tool** | Vite | 7.0 |
| **Auth Scaffold** | Laravel Breeze | 2.3 |
