### How to explain this in the interview:
> "I built a full-stack web application using **Laravel 12** for the backend and **Vue 3** for the frontend, connected through **Inertia.js** which gives us a single-page app experience without building a separate API. The app runs on **MySQL** database and uses **Tailwind CSS** for styling. I use **Vite** as the build tool for fast development."

