```

### How data flows from backend to frontend:
```php
// In a Controller:
return Inertia::render('Cattle/Index', [
    'cattle' => $cattle,      // This becomes a Vue prop
    'filters' => $filters,
]);
```
```vue
<!-- In the Vue page: -->
<script setup>
const props = defineProps({ cattle: Array, filters: Object });
</script>
```

